message.entry: Expected FEATURES1 and FEATURES2 to be the same class.
Expected FEATURES1 and FEATURES2 to have the same number of columns.
The ''MaxRatio'' parameter is only valid when the ''Method'' is ''Exhaustive'' or ''Approximate''.
Parameter ''{0}'' is ignored for binary feature vectors.
The ''Metric'' parameter cannot be set to ''normxcorr'' when the ''Method'' is ''Exhaustive'' or ''Approximate''. Set ''Metric'' to ''SSD'' or ''SAD'' instead.
The ''Method'', ''NearestNeighbor_old'', will be removed in a future release.
The ''Unique'' parameter cannot used with the specified ''Method''. Please set ''Method'' to ''Exhaustive'' or ''Approximate''.
The ''Prenormalized'' parameter is not supported when the ''Method'' is ''Exhaustive'' or ''Approximate''.
The ''Approximate'' method is only supported for MATLAB Host targets. Use the ''Exhaustive'' method instead.
Expected {0} and {1} to have same dimensions.
